show.description: Crown Prince Aarav is forced into a royal marriage with fierce commoner Mira, triggering chaos in the royal palace. As political games unfold and past secrets surface, their clash turns into chemistry, while Rajmata's manipulations threaten to destroy it all. Forever My Prince is a royal romance where duty, love, and rebellion collide. Watch Now!
